headline: Quanta (PWR) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of infrastructure solutions provider Quanta (NYSE:PWR) jumped 3.1% in the afternoon session after the company continued to ride a wave of positive sentiment from recent analyst upgrades and strong business developments.
